OWNERSHIP:
The following components of Alphha Security OS are original works created by
and owned by the Alphha Team:

1. BUILD SYSTEM
   - build-alphha-security.sh (ISO builder)
   - build-alphha-security-vm.sh (VM image builder)
   - alphha-security-spec.json (OS specification)
   - alphha-security-vm-spec.json (VM specification)

2. CUSTOM TOOLS (alphha-toolkit)
   - alphha-recon (reconnaissance automation)
   - alphha-vuln (vulnerability assessment wrapper)
   - alphha-report (security report generator)
   - alphha-backup (forensic evidence collection)
   - alphha-clean (forensic cleanup utility)
   - alphha-menu (security tools launcher)
   - alphha-update (system update utility)

3. INSTALLER
   - alphha-install (TUI installation wizard)

4. BRANDING ASSETS
   - Alphha logo and variations
   - Desktop wallpapers
   - GRUB bootloader theme
   - Plymouth boot splash theme
   - Icon designs

5. DOCUMENTATION
   - User guides
   - Installation documentation
   - Tool documentation

6. CONFIGURATION FILES
   - Security hardening configurations
   - Desktop environment customizations
   - Network configurations

